	   <tr><td colspan=2>The short answer is 'no'.&nbsp;&nbsp;This sword drops from 3rd floor mobs.  A full level 20 group can live down there pretty well but you won't touch the servants down there at 17.  Befallen's mobs will agro you regardless of your level.  I started in befallen around 13 and even at 22 I can still get overpowered in the main room if the whole room agros me.  It's definately a dungeon for groups.<br><br>One thing about this sword that severely limits its value is that it is NO DROP - you can't sell it.  It would only be worth about 75-100p anyway.  Still, it's a decent sword with decent stats.  I keep mine in the bank for corpse runs and it works well.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
